title: Cross-version ValueSet R5.HL7FormatCodes for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version ValueSet represents content from `http://terminology.hl7.org/ValueSet/v3-HL7FormatCodes|1.0.0` for use in FHIR R4.
purpose:
This value set is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
value set `http://terminology.hl7.org/ValueSet/v3-HL7FormatCodes|1.0.0` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

The source value set is bound to the following FHIR R5 elements:
* `DocumentReference.content.profile.value[x]`

The following concepts are not included in this cross-version definition because they have valid representations
* _no concepts_
